label: TYPE
description: This field stores a code that categorizes the contents of this Finance record.

label: DESCRIPTION
description: This field stores the description of the finance item or the name of the creditor.

label: ADDRESS
description: This field stores the address of the creditor.

label: REFERENCE
description: This field stores any reference information about this Finance record.

label: ASSETVALUE
description: This field stores the dollar value of an asset outside the credit union.

label: MONTHLYINCOME
description: This field stores the monthly income of an income outside the credit union.

label: LIABILITYBALANCE
description: This field stores the total liability balance of a liability outside the credit union.

label: MONTHLYEXPENSE
description: This field stores the monthly expense amount of an expense outside the credit union.

label: CREDITLIMIT
description: This field stores the amount of the credit limit of a credit card or a line of credit outside the credit union.

label: INTERESTRATE
description: This field stores the interest rate that is currently being applied to the item in this record.

label: RECORDCHANGEDATE
description: This field stores the date when you create, change, or save the Application Finance record.

label: OWNERCODE
description: This field stores a code that identifies the owner of the asset, liability, or expense in this Finance record.

label: ITEMTYPE
description: This field stores the kind of asset, income, or liability item in this Finance record.

label: DEBTRATIOUSECODE
description: This field stores a code that specifies whether the system should include this Finance record in debt ratio calculations.

label: LIABILITYSTATUS
description: This field stores a code that represents the status of a liability.

label: ASSETSTATUS
description: This field stores a code that represents the status of an asset.

label: USERPLEDGECODE
description: This field stores a code that provides information about whether an item is pledged for another purpose.

label: LOCATOR
description: This field stores a unique number within each member account that can be used as a unique identification of this record.
